snippet.title: Amber Rose Opens Up About Kanye West Like Never Before
snippet.description:
On today's special #EverydayStruggle episode, Amber Rose talked to Joe Budden and DJ Akademiks about the Blac Chyna and Rob Kardashian drama and reveals that she didn't coach Chyna to finesse Rob.
